Book
    page            - array of pages
    active_page()   - function that returns page[bookmark]
    bookmark        - the index of the active page in book
    page_count      - number of pages
    load()          - resets page,bookmark,page_count and replaces them from input file
    flip_page()     - updates bookmark based on the link given from old page

page
    text    - the paragraph text that gets pulled into main_dialog
    options - the text for each of the buttons
    links   - indices for pages to flip to, corresponding to option chosen
    final   - boolean for if this page ends the story. restricts page flipping

GameScreen
    build() - adds main_dialog label; and option[4],ms buttons
SettingsScreen
    build() - adds ms,load_story buttons
MenuScreen
    build() - adds gs,ss buttons
TBA
    build() - adds gs,ss,ms widgets

ScreenSwitchBtn
    on_press() - switches to another screen based on id
OptionBtn
    on_press() - sets 
